t ok to express your faith, or have the right to speak freely and openly about Jesus or the Trinity. Why would I want my kid to go into a school system that is supporting same sex marriages, supporting homosexuality, supporting every single kind of perversion know to man. Plus their is too much corruption inside the school systems today, and they have allowed politics to be a major influence in the school system, instead of focusing on what the main issue is and the is to provide a child an education that they can take out into the real world and be successful. So the real question is why in the world would I want my kid in the public school system, when all they do is blast our faith and beliefs. There is too much corruption inside the public school systems anymore, my question is why in the world do so many other parents tolerate their schools to be filled with chaos and delusions. Public schools systems should be shut down in my opinion and be overhauled completely. Otherwise I will never ever let my kid inside a public school system. "/><type4:DocumentMetaData xmi:id="13" sofa="1" begin="0" end="1361" language="en" documentId="3098" isLastSegment="false"/><types:WebArgumentMetadata xmi:id="24" sofa="1" begin="0" end="0" author="pbracing33b" date="Aug 29, 2013 7:45PM" docType="artcomment" origUrl="http://living.msn.com/family-parenting/the-family-room-blog-post?post=ab228ffc-1e99-4b37-a7b8-0b6a4c3fb240" topic="public-private-schools" thumbsUp="8" thumbsDown="0" origId="3098" notes="" title="Is it wrong to send kids to private school?"/><type6:Paragraph xmi:id="39" sofa="1" begin="0" end="1361"/><cas:View sofa="1" members="13 24 39"/></xmi:XMI>